INSERT INTO `sk_posts` VALUES (12,1,'2016-03-03 08:22:51','2016-03-03 08:22:51','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233\" src=\"http://manishsewaliya.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manish_Sewaliya_Dancer_Salsa_Choreographer_Remo_D_Souza_mini.jpg\" alt=\"Manish Sewaliya Dancer Salsa Choreographer Remo D Souza\" width=\"640\" height=\"852\" />\r\n\r\nManish Sewaliya is a Dance Instructor and Choreographer based out of New Delhi, India.\r\n\r\nFor Manish, dance is his passion for which he lives every moment. As a professional trainer in Western Dance, he loves to infuse energy in others through his technical skills and impeccable dancing style.\r\n\r\nManish has been trained in the following Dance Forms by some of the best international instructors and has extensively worked with highly acclaimed choreographers from the world over\r\n\r\n[su_list]\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Jazz Dance (Afro Jazz, Street Jazz, Funk Jazz, Indo Jazz)</li>\r\n<li>Modern Dance (Contemporary &amp; Modern Contemporary)</li>\r\n<li>Social Dancing (Salsa, Merrengue, Cha Cha, Bachata, Rock & Roll, Jive, Mambo, Tango, Kizomba & Zumba Aerobics)</li>\r\n<li>Freestyle Dance (Bollywood)</li>\r\n<li>Hip Hop Dance (Lyrical Hip Hop, Locking, Poping, Stromping, Krumping, Tuting, B-Boying)</li>\r\n<li>Russian Ballet, Classical Ballet, Belly Dance & Semi Classical</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/su_list]\r\n\r\nDance training and education takes someone only so far. What Manish has achieved having worked with thousands of students and dancers is a thorough knowledge of dance movement and excellent teaching and communication skills. He is known for employing creative techniques to push his students to achieve their true potential. This combined with an intuitive understanding of every dancer\'s needs, allows him to work well as a team and continually push the artistic frontier. ','About','','publish','closed','closed','','about','','','2016-03-20 07:24:54','2016-03-20 07:24:54','',0,'http://manishsewaliya.com/?page_id=12',0,'page','',0),(2,1,'2016-02-29 14:04:45','2016-02-29 14:04:45','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://manishsewaliya.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','trash','closed','open','','sample-page','','','2016-03-09 10:23:35','2016-03-09 10:23:35','',0,'http://manishsewaliya.com/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(245,1,'2016-03-20 07:12:07','2016-03-20 07:12:07','<img src=\"http://manishsewaliya.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manish_Sewaliya_Dancer_Salsa_Choreographer_Remo_D_Souza_mini.jpg\" alt=\"Manish Sewaliya Dancer Salsa Choreographer Remo D Souza\" width=\"640\" height=\"852\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233\" />\r\n\r\nManish Sewaliya is a versatile dancer and choreographer with deep knowledge in a wide range of dance forms. His experience as teacher and choreographer is much sought after and he is a noted Judge on various dance events and shows.\r\n\r\nManish Sewaliya has judged the following dance competitions and events\r\n\r\n[su_list]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Diggy Diggy Dam Dam Dance Competition with Step In Out Academy, Ghaziabad</li>\r\n	<li>Nachle With Rock Star Dance Competition, New Delhi</li>\r\n	<li>Western Dance Competition with St. Vyas Public School, Shalimar Bagh, New Delhi</li>\r\n        <li>Interschool Competition in Bal Bharti Public Sschool, Ghaziabad</li>\r\n        <li>Inter School Competition in Holi Child Auxilium School, R. K. Puram, New Delhi</li>\r\n        <li>Dance Reality Show in Nachle With Future Dance with Sadhna Channel</li>\r\n        <li>Talent Khoj Reality Show with Khoj India Channel in Haryana State</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/su_list]','Dance Judging','','publish','closed','closed','','dance-judging','','','2016-03-20 08:02:32','2016-03-20 08:02:32','',0,'http://manishsewaliya.com/?page_id=245',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2016-03-03 06:39:53','2016-03-03 06:39:53','','Manish Sewaliya Logo','','inherit','open','closed','','manish_sewaliya_logo_mini','','','2016-03-03 06:40:17','2016-03-03 06:40:17','',0,'http://manishsewaliya.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manish_Sewaliya_logo_mini.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5,1,'2016-03-03 06:50:26','2016-03-03 06:50:26','','Manish Sewaliya Icon','','inherit','open','closed','','manish_sewaliya_icon_mini','','','2016-03-03 06:50:46','2016-03-03 06:50:46','',0,'http://manishsewaliya.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manish_Sewaliya_icon_mini.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(6,1,'2016-03-03 07:54:38','2016-03-03 07:54:38','','Manish Sewaliya Dancer Salsa Choreographer','','inherit','open','closed','','manish_sewaliya_dancer_salsa_choreographer5_mini','','','2016-03-03 07:55:54','2016-03-03 07:55:54','',0,'http://manishsewaliya.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manish_Sewaliya_Dancer_Salsa_Choreographer5_mini.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(7,1,'2016-03-03 07:54:41','2016-03-03 07:54:41','','Manish Sewaliya Dancer Salsa Choreographer','','inherit','open','closed','','manish_sewaliya_dancer_salsa_choreographer2_mini','','','2016-03-09 10:22:48','2016-03-09 10:22:48','',16,'http://manishsewaliya.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manish_Sewaliya_Dancer_Salsa_Choreographer2_mini.jpg',