; Modern Contemporary)\r\n Social Dance (Salsa, Merrengue, Cha Cha, Bachata, Rock &amp; Roll, Jive, Mambo, Tango, Kizomba &amp; Zumba Aerobics)\r\n Freestyle Dance (Bollywood)\r\n Hip Hop Dance (Lyrical Hip Hop, Locking, Poping, Stromping, Krumping, Tuting, B-Boying)\r\n Russian Ballet, Classical Ballet, Belly Dance &amp; Semi Classical</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">-&gt; A high level of dancing ability\r\n-&gt; A thorough knowledge of dance and movement\r\n-&gt; Good teaching and communication skills\r\n-&gt; Creativity and imagination\r\n-&gt; Patience, stamina and concentration\r\n-&gt; An understanding of dancers\' needs\r\n-&gt; An understanding of health and safety issues\r\n-&gt; The ability to work well with others</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','12-revision-v1','','','2016-03-03 08:22:51','2016-03-03 08:22:51','',12,'http://manishsewaliya.com/2016/03/03/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(15,1,'2016-03-03 08:26:11','2016-03-03 08:26:11','','cropped-Manish_Sewaliya_Dancer_Salsa_Choreographer5_mini.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','cropped-manish_sewaliya_dancer_salsa_choreographer5_mini-jpg','','','2016-03-09 10:24:42','2016-03-09 10:24:42','',222,'http://manishsewaliya.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/cropped-Manish_Sewaliya_Dancer_Salsa_Choreographer5_mini.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(16,1,'2016-03-03 08:31:43','2016-03-03 08:31:43','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7\" src=\"http://manishsewaliya.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manish_Sewaliya_Dancer_Salsa_Choreographer2_mini.jpg\" alt=\"Manish Sewaliya Dancer Salsa Choreographer\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" />\r\n\r\nManish Sewaliya is a popular Dance Choreographer and Instructor in schools, colleges and event organizers in Delhi. His excellent grasp on a wide repertoire of dance styles and communication skills makes him a highly sought after Dance Choreographer for dancers of all ages and backgrounds. \r\n\r\nManish has choreographed Dance In Education and Annual Days in the following schools\r\n\r\n[su_list icon=\"icon: arrow-right\"]<ul>\r\n<li>Spring Dales School, Pusa Road, New Delhi</li>\r\n<li>Mira Model School, Janak Puri, New Delhi</li>\r\n<li>G.D Goenka School, Dwarka, New Delhi</li>\r\n<li>Gargi Girls School, Meerut</li>\r\n<li>Ravindra Public School, Shakti Nagar, New Delhi</li>\r\n<li>Choreograph Annual Day 2011 of G.D Goenka School, Dwarka</li>\r\n<li>Choreograph Annual Day 2011 of I.T.L. Public School, Dwarka</li>\r\n<li>Choreograph Annual Day 2011 of Indraprastha World School, Paschim Vihar</li>\r\n<li>Choreograph Annual Day 2011 of Ravindra Public School, Shakti Nagar</li>\r\n<li>Choreograph Annual Day 2013 of St. Marks Sen. Sec School, Meera Bagh</li>\r\n<li>Choreograph Sports Day 2013 &amp; 2014 of Delhi Public School, Vasant Kunj</li>\r\n<li>Choreograph Independence Day 2014 Function in Dayanand Model School, CP</li>\r\n<li>Choreograph Global Kids Fashion Show 2013 for Quick Step</li>\r\n</ul>[/su_list]\r\n\r\nIn a long career spanning a decade, Manish has worked and collaborated with some of the best dancers and choreographers in the Industry. Noteworthy among these are his works with Bollywood Singer Sukhwinder Singh and as a Choreographer in Bollywood movie Jackpot Pe Jackpot under Cinema 18 Motion Pictures production house. Manish is an internal part of The Hindustan Times – Pace as their resource person and has been conducting Western Dance Workshops for more than 1600 schools in and around Delhi NCR organized by HT–PACE.','Dance Choreography','','publish','closed','closed','','dance-choreography','','','2016-03-20 08:24:49','2016-03-20 08:24:49','',0,'http://manishsewaliya.com/?page_id=16',0,'page','',0),(17,1,'2016-03-03 08:31:43','2016-03-03 08:31:43',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','17','','','2016-03-20 08:00:24','2016-03-20 08:00:24','',0,'http://manishsewaliya.com/2016/03/03/17/',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(18,1,'2016-03-03 08:31:43','2016-03-03 08:31:4